#: src-en/data/dlcEvents.xml.append:7
msgid "data/dlcEvents.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FUEL_ESCAPE_PULSAR\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"Taking advantage of the last of your fuel reserves, you were able to "
"navigate to a safe distance from the pulsar."

#: src-en/data/dlcEvents.xml.append:11
msgid "data/dlcEvents.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FUEL_ESCAPE_PDS\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"Using your impulse engines, you were able to pull to a safe distance from "
"the hostile planet."

#: src-en/data/dlcEvents.xml.append:15
msgid "data/dlcEvents.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FUEL_ESCAPE_FLEET\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"Your pilot deftly avoids the artillery fire from the surrounding fleet while"
" you try to sort out exactly what your plan is...."

#: src-en/data/dlcEvents.xml.append:34
msgid "data/dlcEvents.xml.append$//event[@name=\"REBEL_PULSAR\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/dlcEvents.xml.append:39
msgid "data/dlcEvents.xml.append$//textList[@name=\"REBEL_PULSAR_TEXT\"]/text[1]"
msgstr ""
"A Rebel captain appears on the screen. \"I thought we had been doomed to "
"backwater assignments. This is my chance to get back in Command's good "
"graces! Charge the weapons!\""

#: src-en/data/dlcEvents.xml.append:40
msgid "data/dlcEvents.xml.append$//textList[@name=\"REBEL_PULSAR_TEXT\"]/text[2]"
msgstr ""
"A small rebel research station overlooks a pulsating star. Before you can "
"react a Rebel ship spots you and moves in to attack."

#: src-en/data/dlcEvents.xml.append:41
msgid "data/dlcEvents.xml.append$//textList[@name=\"REBEL_PULSAR_TEXT\"]/text[3]"
msgstr ""
"You arrive at an infrequently used beacon close to a pulsar. Before long a "
"Rebel ship happens to jump nearby. Looks like you'll have to fight."

#: src-en/data/dlcEvents.xml.append:49
msgid "data/dlcEvents.xml.append$//event[@name=\"PIRATE_PULSAR\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/dlcEvents.xml.append:54
msgid "data/dlcEvents.xml.append$//textList[@name=\"PIRATE_PULSAR_TEXT\"]/text[1]"
msgstr ""
"Sensors go wild as a nearby pulsar is detected. While you are attempting to "
"recalibrate the FTL drive, a pirate sneaks up on your ship, weapons "
"charging. Prepare for a fight!"

#: src-en/data/dlcEvents.xml.append:55
msgid "data/dlcEvents.xml.append$//textList[@name=\"PIRATE_PULSAR_TEXT\"]/text[2]"
msgstr ""
"You arrive to find a pulsar dominating the view screen. You see a small "
"silhouette pass in front of the star. Before you can ponder what it is, "
"warning signals go off. It appears to be a ship in a firing trajectory!"

#: src-en/data/dlcEvents.xml.append:56
msgid "data/dlcEvents.xml.append$//textList[@name=\"PIRATE_PULSAR_TEXT\"]/text[3]"
msgstr ""
"A small research station orbits a nearby pulsar. It appears largely "
"abandoned, but you detect power signatures flaring up as soon as you're in "
"scanning distance. A small combat ship launches from the station. Pirates!"

#: src-en/data/dlcEvents.xml.append:64
msgid "data/dlcEvents.xml.append$//event[@name=\"REBEL_PDS\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Prepare to fight."

